19:45:22.000Z","msg":"我都成日拗柴 本身隻腳又生得衰啲<br />\n之前有次去咗睇骨科(但我骨無事<br />\n佢轉介咗我去睇物理治療<br />\n嗰陣唔記得係咪個醫生定先治療師叫我買呢隻<br />\n<a href=\"https://24h.pchome.com.tw/prod/DEAQ8D-A9005RCZH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F24h.pchome.com.tw%2Fprod%2FDEAQ8D-A9005RCZH&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6KVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=c32a5413\" target=\"_blank\">https://24h.pchome.com.tw/prod/DEAQ8D-A9005RCZH</a><br />\n類似咁嘅強力繃帶去承托住隻腳(無護踝套) <br />\n<br />\n建議樓主去睇醫生再等轉介信或直接睇物理治療"},{"pid":"84c247535c199b04af4a40827d5c2cddd2d37224","tid":2122142,"uid":236855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"687b56f49c00bae0bed1365cbb430419157fe28c","tid":2122142,"uid":10566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:59:08.000Z","msg":"除咗腫咗之外<br />\n腳掌放鬆嗰陣係向內彎得好犀利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T20:08:03.000Z","msg":"睇骨科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係拗完好番個陣生唔啱位，一係根本未好過<br />\n唔洗問照一照xray最清楚知咩事"},{"pid":"224e071be3313d2b95332556923c68ebae66fd6a","tid":2122142,"uid":36364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T20:23:29.000Z","msg":"過來人 睇過跌打 係垃圾嚟 傷咗成年 最後要照x ray再搵個夾嘅物理治療 先好返 都唔係100% <br />\n<br />\n樓主唔好再拖 快快脆照x ray先"},{"pid":"f1a4c311bf94c44324f3d853ea4a1be855938aae","tid":2122142,"uid":51735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T20:28:24.000Z","msg":"咁你應該都幾嚴重 我幾年前都係咁 又係睇跌打 不過應該冇你咁嚴重 但係我時不時行路隻腳都會啪啪聲 都跳唔到以前咁高"},{"pid":"89e5daf24dba94ca3eb4cab07b2430fb3ae98882","tid":2122142,"uid":114064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:21:50.000Z","msg":"你當時處理不當，現已成舊患"},{"pid":"194a16b04b56efbe7146f528ce1ae7cc59e697d5","tid":2122142,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人都係追巴士拗柴 有冇咁撚廢"},{"pid":"e51ab58791c64b9950f2fb8c24e8d65207d046f9","tid":2122142,"uid":10566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"194a16b04b56efbe7146f528ce1ae7cc59e697d5","tid":2122142,"uid":3