後就唔敢跑步<br />\n<br />\n之前都係睇中醫 跌打<br />\n想轉睇物理治療 睇吓可唔可以醫返好<br />\n有冇好醫生介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"肥唔肥？<br />\n<br />\n肥既要減。拗開真係有條路，試下帶護腕踝套得唔得？"},{"pid":"1bcd735597d5f47bcff2992a0b2fe1a150a0e001","tid":2122142,"uid":345295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:14:32.000Z","msg":"3年前拗柴到宜家都未好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初拗柴我發現腳眼凹咗好似移咗位，去咗公立學校睇咗2次，2次都有照x ray，結果都係冇料到，嗰2次幫我診症嘅唔係醫生係護士長，個護士長話係因為我仲腫緊，消腫就冇事，話腳眼冇移位，叫我唔好諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果消腫之後腳眼真係凹咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前拗柴嘅後遺症仲係度，腳腫腳震腳掌伸唔直，如果平訓唔用力腳掌會斜咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好sad啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f1c089e02c18de194b0c8c0f807e1ee851dd9b","tid":2122142,"uid":345295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bcd735597d5f47bcff2992a0b2fe1a150a0e001","tid":2122142,"uid":345295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:14:32.000Z","msg":"3年前拗柴到宜家都未好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初拗柴我發現腳眼凹咗好似移咗位，去咗公立學校睇咗2次，2次都有照x ray，結果都係冇料到，嗰2次幫我診症嘅唔係醫生係護士長，個護士長話係因為我仲腫緊，消腫就冇事，話腳眼冇移位，叫我唔好諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果消腫之後腳眼真係凹咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前拗柴嘅後遺症仲係度，腳腫腳震腳掌伸唔直，如果平訓唔用力腳掌會斜咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好sad啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"當時拗柴之後冇耐就神經性休克，頭暈眼花之後視線仲黑9埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要想嘔心跳加速耳鳴，真係好想死，嗰陣我仲以為係中暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人生未試過咁多痛苦嘅特徴一齊出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第二日結果落唔到床，一郁就痛撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拗柴之後腳側邊仲要有瘀血，第一次拗柴拗到懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望我嘅人生唔會再有拗柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想2隻腳都殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5618f0057d2e7f24fd5aa856c1e6fed0739e45db","tid":2122142,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:25:04.000Z","msg":"訓練屎忽肌肉可以防止拗柴<br />\nNBA嗰個Curry都係練完之後<br />\n由玻璃腳變咗鐵人"},{"pid":"07f1cabb2b43c5223f1b78c9f26985ae011776a0","tid":2122142,"uid":307732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"拗柴後淨係睇跌打點會得 踝關節而家一定唔穩定 好容易再受傷 去照下片 x光先啦 有需要再照mri 做物理治療都ok 架"},{"pid":"ae0de99065db77731488ae44af53df1e2f90ea95","tid":2122142,"uid":214042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bcd735597d5f47bcff2992a0b2fe1a150a0e001","tid":2122142,"uid":345295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:14:32.000Z","msg":"3年前拗柴到宜家都未好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初拗柴我發現腳眼凹咗好似移咗位，去咗公立學校睇咗2次，2次都有照x ray，結果都係冇料到，嗰2次幫我診症嘅唔係醫生係護士長，個護士長話係因為我仲腫緊，消腫就冇事，話腳眼冇移位，叫我唔好諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果消腫之後腳眼真係凹咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前拗柴嘅後遺症仲係度，腳腫腳震腳掌伸唔直，如果平訓唔用力腳掌會斜咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好sad啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:27:46.000Z","msg":"影黎睇下"}]}